excalidraw-vendor
=================

This directory is a self-contained, fully-offline build of Excalidraw's
`exportToSvg`, plus its Latin font files. The renderer serves it over a loopback
HTTP server, so a diagram render never touches the network and can never break
from CDN dependency drift.

Pinned versions (regenerate deliberately — never implicitly):
  @excalidraw/excalidraw : 0.18.1
  bundled with esbuild   : 0.28.1
  node                   : v22.18.0
  generated              : 2026-07-07

Contents:
  excalidraw.mjs   single-file ESM bundle exporting exportToSvg (~8 MB).
                   NOT committed — fetched once on first render from a pinned,
                   sha256-verified GitHub Release (see bundle.lock.json) and
                   cached here. Rebuild + republish with scripts/vendor.sh.
  bundle.lock.json integrity pin (release url + sha256) — committed.
  fonts/           Latin font families used by Excalidraw text — committed.

Deliberately excluded: the Xiaolai CJK font family (~12 MB of woff2 subset
chunks). Technical/English diagrams never use it. If you need CJK glyphs, edit
scripts/build.mjs to stop dropping Xiaolai and re-run scripts/vendor.sh.

To bump the pinned version, run:  ../scripts/vendor.sh <version>
(see that script for the full, reproducible recipe).
